{"type": "article", "id": 5240, "title": "飞鱼椅 Exocet Chair", "description": "", "date": "2015-01-15T07:59:27Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 35, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606152620te9kfuxlYXqZgQ4d.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t在本月底的加拿大多伦多室内设计展(Interior Design Show)上，家具设计品牌 Designarium 将带来他们的第一款作品 Exocet Chair。在法语里，「Exocet 」是飞鱼的意思，设计团队亦是以飞鱼作为原型，选用自然原木材质，赋予了这把椅子流畅的线条与轮廓，就像在水中游动的鱼儿一样。他们将鱼头作为杠杆的中心，可以把尾巴翻转至任何想要的角度，立起尾巴来可以变身高椅背，也可以横放于地上，变成躺椅、椅凳等。坐、卧、躺或是趴，满足你各种任性的需求。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152618Ye7zVd0EM4KQq8oS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152618LUJftGy5krj1TnuO.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152619JPqXcdx5o0OR9kI3.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061526195mFKaiy18YSZhjRd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606152619yNXJhKpOcxRl9z1I.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.665625\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}